  "description": "A dramatic image of the Mackinac Bridge silhouetted against a fiery sunset over water. The bridge appears as a dark shape with only faint visible details, framed by the dark, leafy branches of trees in the foreground. The sun is positioned directly behind the bridge, creating a bright, golden glow that radiates outwards. The water reflects some of the orange and red hues from the sky, while the rest remains dark and shadowy. The overall effect is one of stark contrast and dramatic beauty.",
